themes: Time constraints for artists with families
Financial barriers due to rising ticket prices
key_phrases: The biggest barrier is making time for it.
As a full time musician with a family, my availability to access the arts is limited.
Ticket prices and events have gradually gone up and sometimes it's not in the budget to make some of these events.
Parking at some events is challenging, especially downtown.
barriers_identified: Limited time due to family and work obligations
